          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-white">
            Away from the keyboard he&apos;s usually grilling something,
            building something out of wood, or pretending his home projects have
            a deadline. Downtime means hanging with his fiancé Hannah, a dog
            named Hank who thinks he&apos;s a person, and two cats, Gus and
            Bernie, who are definitely in charge. Soundtrack: strictly Yacht
            Rock.
          </p>
        </div>
